### AI Translation: translate existing key from en -> fr (sourceText inferred from en.json)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/i18n/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "product.addToCart",
  "targetLang": "es",
  "sourceLang": "en"
}

###

### AI Translation: translate with explicit sourceText (bypasses en.json lookup)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/i18n/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "home.hero.slide1.title",
  "sourceText": "Elevate Your Style",
  "targetLang": "fr",
  "sourceLang": "en"
}

###

### AI Translation: error case (missing key)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/i18n/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "",
  "targetLang": "fr"
}

